      <prop type="x-translation-ref">河廣.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>誰謂河廣，一葦杭之，誰謂宋遠，跂予望之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>How wide is the Ho!
Yet it may be passed in a raft.
That Song is far off,
Yet it may be reached by a day's journey.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
