      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>誰謂河廣，曾不容刀，誰謂宋遠，曾不崇朝。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>How wide is the Ho!
Yet it may be passed in a boat.
That Song is far off,
Yet it may be reached by fording.</seg>
